  <p>Your track is live. Now what?</p>

  <h3>Monitor your name across platforms</h3>
  <p>New artists emerge every day. Someone could release under a similar name after you. The TruClarify monitoring service checks your artist name weekly and alerts you to new conflicts — so you catch problems before they damage your catalogue.</p>

