  <h3>Build your short-form video presence</h3>
  <p>TikTok and Reels are how AI music goes viral. A 15-second clip showing your Suno prompt → the reveal → your finished track is consistently one of the highest-performing formats for AI music creators. The Premium Pipeline Kit includes a complete video engine with scripts and hooks tailored to your genre.</p>

