  <h2>Common Questions</h2>

  <h3>Can Suno music be on Spotify?</h3>
  <p>Yes — on a paid Suno plan, with proper AI disclosure during upload. Spotify allows AI-generated music but prohibits content designed to imitate specific human artists. Tick the AI content checkbox on your distributor upload form and you're compliant.</p>

  <h3>How long does it take for Suno music to appear on Spotify?</h3>
