  <h2>The Honest Bottom Line</h2>

  <p>Do you own music made with Suno? Here's where I land:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>You own a <strong>commercial licence</strong> to use it — on a paid plan</li>
    <li>You may own <strong>copyright in the human-authored elements</strong> — lyrics, recordings, arrangement decisions</li>
